are working in our field.

300
00:13:09,771 --> 00:13:10,890
What a pity.

301
00:13:12,331 --> 00:13:14,290
Although you ranked top in medical school

302
00:13:14,291 --> 00:13:15,210
and gained some

303
00:13:15,531 --> 00:13:17,210
clinical experience from me,

304
00:13:18,291 --> 00:13:19,090
but

305
00:13:19,211 --> 00:13:20,170
you're a woman

306
00:13:20,891 --> 00:13:21,810
and a newcomer.

307
00:13:22,531 --> 00:13:23,890
I'm afraid some patients

308
00:13:23,891 --> 00:13:25,050
might have prejudices.

309
00:13:26,451 --> 00:13:27,170
How about this:

310
00:13:27,771 --> 00:13:29,450
sign a six-month

311
00:13:29,531 --> 00:13:30,690
probationary period with the hospital.

312
00:13:31,451 --> 00:13:32,650
Spend some time

313
00:13:32,651 --> 00:13:33,810
in the general medicine department

314
00:13:33,811 --> 00:13:34,810
to gain more experience.

315
00:13:35,091 --> 00:13:35,890
After a while,

316
00:13:36,211 --> 00:13:36,810
I'll transfer you

317
00:13:37,051 --> 00:13:37,890
to the OB/GYN department.

318
00:13:38,531 --> 00:13:39,890
They are short-staffed there.

319
00:13:40,411 --> 00:13:41,770
Thank you so much, Dean Lin.

320
00:13:45,531 --> 00:13:47,410
But I have a small request.

321
00:13:47,931 --> 00:13:48,530
Go ahead.

322
00:13:52,411 --> 00:13:53,090
Dean Lin,

323
00:13:53,931 --> 00:13:56,090
I've already left the Zhou family.

324
00:13:56,571 --> 00:13:58,210
I'd like to apply for a hospital dormitory.

325
00:14:02,771 --> 00:14:03,530
The medical school

326
00:14:04,091 --> 00:14:05,290
producing a female doctor

327
00:14:06,211 --> 00:14:07,170
brings me great joy.

328
00:14:07,771 --> 00:14:08,330
Rest assured,

329
00:14:08,691 --> 00:14:09,450
no problem.

330
00:14:10,651 --> 00:14:11,530
Thank you, Dean Lin.

331
00:14:26,451 --> 00:14:27,170
Dr. Ye, a patient

332
00:14:27,931 --> 00:14:29,330
is waiting in the examination room.

333
00:14:30,091 --> 00:14:30,650
I'll be right there.

334
00:14:32,211 --> 00:14:32,770
Dr. Ye,

335
00:14:33,691 --> 00:14:34,530
be careful.

336
00:14:48,531 --> 00:14:49,330
What are you doing?

337
00:14:49,331 --> 00:14:50,210
Doctor,

338
00:14:50,531 --> 00:14:51,810
I just want you to help me

339
00:14:51,811 --> 00:14:53,210
check another area.

340
00:14:53,891 --> 00:14:54,770
My chest here

341
00:14:55,211 --> 00:14:55,890
for some reason

342
00:14:56,331 --> 00:14:58,210
started hurting badly after seeing you.

343
00:14:58,531 --> 00:14:59,450
This heart...

344
00:15:00,451 --> 00:15:01,330
Don't leave!

345
00:15:01,531 --> 00:15:02,330
What are you doing?

346
00:15:02,331 --> 00:15:02,810
Rub it for me.

347
00:15:03,091 --> 00:15:04,090
Let go of me!
- Rub it.

348
00:15:04,771 --> 00:15:05,890
Aren't you a doctor?

349
00:15:05,891 --> 00:15:07,290
You can't just leave someone to die!

350
00:15:08,651 --> 00:15:09,450
Let me go!

351
00:15:11,331 --> 00:15:12,650
The injection site hurts again.

352
00:15:12,891 --> 00:15:13,890
Here!

353
00:15:14,171 --> 00:15:15,330
Rub it!

354
00:15:16,531 --> 00:15:18,170
That spot where I got the injection...

355
00:15:18,571 --> 00:15:19,090
Look.

356
00:15:20,531 --> 00:15:21,290
Don't move!

357
00:15:21,891 --> 00:15:23,410
If the needle breaks inside,

358
00:15:23,411 --> 00:15:24,530
surgery will be complicated.

359
00:15:29,171 --> 00:15:29,970
Need I say

360
00:15:30,331 --> 00:15:31,610
military discipline twice?

361
00:15:32,531 --> 00:15:32,930
Go!

362
00:15:41,051 --> 00:15:41,770
Thank you!

363
00:15:46,051 --> 00:15:46,890
What are you doing here?

364
00:15:50,091 --> 00:15:51,450
Why didn't you tell me

365
00:15:52,411 --> 00:15:53,210
you left the Zhou residence?

366
00:15:53,891 --> 00:15:55,410
I just left the Zhou family

367
00:15:55,411 --> 00:15:56,530
a couple of days ago.

368
00:15:57,091 --> 00:15:58,170
You're starting over.

369
00:15:59,571 --> 00:16:00,090
Close the door.

370
00:16:00,571 --> 00:16:00,930
Yes!

371
00:16:08,211 --> 00:16:09,090
What do you mean by this?

372
00:16:09,931 --> 00:16:10,810
Help me check my injury.

373
00:16:17,931 --> 00:16:19,770
Why are you covered in wounds?

374
00:16:23,211 --> 00:16:24,450
Your wounds are too deep.

375
00:16:24,531 --> 00:16:25,530
Let me treat them for you.

376
00:16:25,531 --> 00:16:26,450
Or it might get infected.

377
00:16:40,051 --> 00:16:40,450
Done.

378
00:16:48,411 --> 00:16:49,450
Can I come to you

379
00:16:50,451 --> 00:16:51,450
if I get hurt in the future?

380
00:16:52,891 --> 00:16:54,090
Come back in three days to change the dressing.

381
00:16:54,451 --> 00:16:55,570
Keep the wounds dry.

382
00:17:03,091 --> 00:17:03,930
Where are you going after work?

383
00:17:07,851 --> 00:17:08,930
Exit and turn right to pay.

384
00:17:14,531 --> 00:17:16,330
Are you already with Zhou Yimo?

385
00:17:20,611 --> 00:17:21,130
Let go.

386
00:17:22,531 --> 00:17:23,290
Answer me.

387
00:17:25,811 --> 00:17:26,410
Yes.

388
00:17:27,411 --> 00:17:28,530
We are together.

389
00:17:28,771 --> 00:17:29,810
So please conduct yourself properly,

390
00:17:29,811 --> 00:17:30,530
Lieutenant Yu!
